  "instructions": [
    "Combine seafood mix, chili flakes, tomato paste, garlic, ginger, lemon juice, and Kasik in a claypot.",
    "Mix well to coat seafood evenly.",
    "Cover claypot and steam over medium heat for 8 minutes, or until seafood is opaque and flakes easily with a fork.",
    "Stir in parsley and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Serve hot with bread, and optional butter and salt.",
    "Garnish with extra parsley if desired.",
    "Serve immediately, and enjoy!",
    "Note: If using frozen seafood, thaw according to package instructions before cooking."
